{"tid":1405673,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 祖記年青前鋒kean正式加盟愛華頓","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:43:27.000Z","uid":153600,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"683a6e6b5e8833f60a49128fd9db74b4a33ddfdd","tid":1405673,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"EVERTON SIGN STRIKER KEAN<br />\n<br />\nBy Howard Frost<br />\n<br />\nExpand<br />\n<br />\nMoise Kean has signed for Everton from Juventus for an undisclosed fee, agreeing a five-year deal until the end of June 2024.<br />\nThe 19-year-old Italy international striker &ndash; regarded as one of the brightest young talents in Europe &ndash; becomes the Blues&rsquo; fifth summer signing after midfielders Andre Gomes, Fabian Delph and Jean-Philippe Gbamin and keeper Jonas L&ouml;ssl.<br />\nKean says he is honoured to join Everton and wants to bring his winning attitude to a club that matches his ambition.<br />\n&ldquo;I am very proud and honoured to wear the Everton shirt. I will give my best to this team,&rdquo; Kean told evertontv.<br />\n&ldquo;I was convinced to sign because Everton is a club looking to the future and so am I. I know about the size of the Club. It has big ambition and I will work very hard to help us fulfil what we want to achieve.<br />\n&ldquo;I am used to winning and I want to bring this winning attitude to the team. I hope I will be very good on the field and bring the fans joy.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.evertonfc.com/news/1300376/everton-sign-striker-kean\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.evertonfc.com%2Fnews%2F1300376%2Feverton-sign-striker-kean&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUByPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=6028e8bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.evertonfc.com/news/1300376/everton-sign-striker-kean</a>"},{"pid":"cfb9da664e355f2058aff39b72d133d31881b7b1","tid":1405673,"uid":5649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":